Description:
Luxurious & Spacious With stunning harbour views !
Encompassing a huge master bedroom with walk in robes and ensuite with his and her basins, second bedroom with mirrored built in robes, central bathroom with full sized bath and separate shower, massive kitchen with walk in pantry and a massive open plan living/dining area perfect for entertainers make this home one not to be looked over.
Situated 22 floors above the picturesque Docklands the property features a West facing balcony running the full length of the apartment and flooding the entire property with natural light while providing breathtaking views of the harbour and Docklands precinct. Additional features include ducted heating and cooling, tasteful furnishings throughout, a secure car space, intercom as well as the building facilities such as concierge and security entrance.
Walk to South Wharf promenade with restaurants and bars including Citizen Café and Bar, Melbourne Public, Bangpop, and Munich Brauhaus. You’re also near the Victoria Harbour precinct, Crown Entertainment Complex with world class restaurants, Port Melbourne and South Melbourne attractions, and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Paradise for investors or owner occupiers in the sublime Marina Tower building
Sitting high on the 25th floor of the sought-after Marina Tower, this brand new one bedroom apartment will strike a chord with passionate Docklands buyers on the hunt for a modern and easy care retreat which delivers amazing city and Victoria Harbour views.
Whether youre an investor or an owner-occupier, youll fall head over heels for this apartment which promises terrific attention to detail and sublime quality throughout. Buyers will get to enjoy a bright central lounge and meals zone with the city, water, and Marvel Stadium as your constant backdrop, elegant stone kitchen with Miele appliances, covered balcony also with excellent vistas, generous bedroom with BIR, stylish bathroom, study nook off the entry, European laundry, reverse cycle cooling, and secure intercom.
Youll get exclusive access to an opulent lobby lounge which will dazzle upon entry, as well as a library, private business centre, meeting rooms, cinema, lounge and billiard room, kitchen and dining area, rooftop pool, gym, and expansive deck. Take advantage of nearby habrourside restaurants and cafes, The District Docklands, Ron Barassi Snr Park, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and the 35, 70, and 86 trams giving you access all across Melbourne.
To arrange an inspection, please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 or Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556.

Description:
Simply Stunning Dock 5 Lifestyle with 2 Oversized Outdoor Areas
Distinctive designer finishes, a breathtaking Victoria Harbour outlook, and two oversized outdoor areas define this dramatically daring 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment in the luxury-led Dock 5 building. The exceptional lifestyle appeal is undeniable with Victoria Harbour on your doorstep and easy walking distance to free city trams, Woolworths shopping, and NewQuay restaurants.
Designed for easy living, discover a welcoming entrance hallway branching off to a super-sleek Smeg kitchen with integrated microwave, gleaming granite benchtops, and a Bosch dishwasher. Enjoy far-reaching, open-plan living and dining, offering a seamless connection to a full-width undercover balcony on one side and a roomy courtyard in a garden setting on the other. Blissfully boasting light and airy cross-ventilation, both of these outdoor areas are an entertainers dream with the added bonus of a blue-water panorama from the balcony. Both large bedrooms are equipped with extensive built-in robes and the main bedroom comes complete with its own fully tiled ensuite and private balcony access.
Freshly painted and carpeted throughout, special features include a fully tiled bathroom with a double concealed laundry, secure parking, ducted heating/cooling, and video intercom entry. The Dock 5 building boasts first-class, resort-style facilities including a 25 metre lap pool, fully fitted gym, and a BBQ garden terrace. Experience luxury living at every turn and make this exceptional apartment your home, city base or blue-chip investment today!
* Photo identification will be required upon entering the property at the inspection time.

Description:
WATERFRONT GEM - Approx 100 sq m.
Bathed in natural light with captivating views across the Yarra, Marina and bay is this immaculate spacious apartment in the most sought after and arguably best located building in Docklands (Flinders Wharf). Approx 100 sq m.
Offering the discerning buyer the comforts of 2 generous size bedrooms, master with walk-in robes and en-suite, main bathroom has a deep relaxing bath with overhead shower, large living/dining adjoining modern kitchen with quality stainless steel Smeg kitchen appliances, stone bench tops and ample cupboard space. Other features include central heating and cooling, floor to ceiling windows, fabulous balcony providing outlook across the Yarra & Port Philip Bay, 1 secure under cover car space and resident access to the fabulous facilities which include a heated indoor lap pool, spa, sauna, steam-room and gymnasium.
The building is within walking distance to tram (Free Zone), train, South Wharf, DFO, Crown Casino and all the beauty that Melbourne has to offer.
For inspection call Richard 0437 250 964

Deadline Private Sale Closing Tuesday 28 May at 5.00pm
Stylish waterside apartment offers exciting Melbourne lifestyle
Located in the prestigous Yarra's edge overlooking the Yarra River & Docklands Marina, this perfectly positioned two-bedroom apartment offers an unrivalled waterside lifestyle with easy access to South Wharf Promenade, Crown Casino & just a short stroll to the CBD. The layout comprises a generous open-plan kitchen with Smeg appliances & stone bench tops overlooking the spacious living area with stylish timber floors, glazed water views, saturated in northern light while creating a seamless transition between the interior & generous balcony which runs the entire length of the apartment, perfect for entertaining. With an elegant contemporary aesthetic, waterside location & close proximity to some of Melbournes most loved attractions, this magnificent apartment offers a unique & fulfilling Melbourne lifestyle.

Description:
LIFESTYLE WATERFRONT LIVING AT ITS BEST!
Nestled on the 13th floor of the amazing Conder residential complex, this building is perfectly situated at the head of Newquay Promenade. There is an air of style to this spacious apartment offering open-plan living, dining, and kitchen which is ideal for entertaining.
The main bedroom, including a large walk-in wardrobe, is complemented by a stylish ensuite with a clean, modern finish, plus a balcony that drinks in breathtaking views of Victoria Harbour. The remaining bedroom with mirrored BIRs also come complete with floor to ceiling windows of spectacular harbour views. Complementing this is the beautiful stone benchtops in the kitchen and bathrooms, Euro-laundry, ducted heating & cooling, double glazed windows, secure swipe & intercom entry, and two secured car spaces to round out this sophisticated residence.
Building features include an onsite gym, pool, sauna, and barbecue area, this is executive, low maintenance living at its most exceptional. With free public transport, Marvel Stadium, a world-class shopping precinct District Docklands, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on your doorstep, this must-see apartment is perfectly situated only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.

Description:
MARVELOUS DOCKLANDS APARTMENT
On offer is this beautifully presented opportunity for investors or owner occupiers alike in this 2 bed, 1 bath apartment in the chic M Docklands complex. This beautifully contemporary apartment comes with remarkable styling, and finishes.
The open plan kitchen/dining area includes a stone bench-top island with breakfast bar, concealed dishwasher, Bosch oven and cooktop, concealed fridge, and plenty of clever storage solutions. The light-filled living room flows out onto the balcony with views of the CBD and Marvel Stadium. Both bedrooms come with mirrored BIRs.

Rounding out this remarkable apartment is a Euro-laundry, secure swipe and video intercom entry, secure car space, and storage cage. In addition to these amenities, residents can take advantage of Peppers Privileges such as home delivery from the Momami Restaurant and vehicle detailing.
With public transport, world class shopping, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on your doorstep, this inner city pad is perfectly situated on La Trobe Street where Docklands meets the CBD, and is only minutes from the CBD and City Link.

Description:
Unmatched, Uninterrupted, North-Facing Views in the Lap of Dock 5 Luxury
Cleverly combining light-filled, loft-style luxury with a genuine feeling of warmth and inclusion, this striking 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom apartment will exceed expectations from the very first step inside. Spectacularly spread over two levels on the 26th floor of the tightly held Dock 5 building, you could not wish for a more impeccable lifestyle address with Victoria Harbour on your doorstep and easy access to Woolworths shopping, city-bound trams, and NewQuay restaurants and cafes.
Discover a remarkably roomy open-plan living and dining area, making the most of full-height, full-width glass. Fronting the apartment over both floors, this imposing wall of windows directs northern light to every far-reaching corner, maximising the views of Victoria Harbour and beyond. Complementing all this space, a marble-finished kitchen boasts an integrated suite of high-end Smeg appliances and an entertainers breakfast bar featuring dining capacity.
Facing north in a commanding position, enjoy a sheltered balcony overlooking Victoria Harbour with breathtaking views of Bolte Bridge and Marvel Stadium. This instantly relaxing location is the perfect spot to take stock, no matter the time of day or night with the Melbourne Star acting as a thrilling centrepiece.
Supremely styled in a palette of neutral tones, a generously sized and privately staged downstairs bedroom showcases a sleek wall of built-in robes, balcony water views, and a tempting, twin-vanity ensuite with a sumptuous spa bath.
Head upstairs to the remaining bedrooms and so much more. A wide-reaching retreat shares in all the spectacular views in a mezzanine setting, while a home office with dedicated built-in desk space is fit for a workforce. The pair of bedrooms feature extensive built-in robes, while the larger of the two offers private balcony access and a fully tiled ensuite with a bath and walk-in shower. Another fully tiled bathroom and a concealed laundry with a Fisher and Paykel dryer completes the upstairs picture.
Timeless, elegant and uncompromisingly sophisticated, enjoy flawless finishes and a relaxed and refined lifestyle on the waters edge. Take advantage of a ground-floor powder room, 3 side-by-side car spaces, ducted heating and refrigerated cooling, a selection of remote-controlled Holland blinds from top to bottom, and a range of stylish storage solutions throughout.
Popular with owner-occupiers and masterfully designed by multi-award-winning architect John Wardle, the Dock 5 building boasts world-class, resort-style facilities including a temperature-controlled wine cellar, 25 metre lap pool, fully fitted gym, a BBQ garden terrace, and a stately library. Astute buyers will need to act decisively as this one will not last long!
* Photo identification will be required upon entering the property at the inspection time.

Description:
A Serious NewQuay Contender with Startling Water Vistas
The stunning Boyd Tower provides the luxury and immaculate setting for this exceptional 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom corner apartment, which produces some of the most sun-filled and stylish Docklands accommodation as well as unforgettable views of the scenic Victoria Harbour.
Wake up each morning and appreciate all the brilliant living highlights this 17th floor apartment has to offer. The bright full windows and corner location allows for irresistible views of the harbour as well as Marvel Stadium and the iconic CBD right from the comfort of the spacious lounge and dining hub. For those who love fresh air, the balcony will be your 2nd home for outdoor dining or just soaking in the tranquil views.
Sleek stone benchtops, glass splashback, and stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher are the highlights of the beautiful kitchen. Three bedrooms all boast a relaxed feel including the master bedroom which has a walk-in robe and gorgeous ensuite. Other apartment features include main bathroom with separate powder room, European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, intercom, storage cage, secure car space, and access to a BBQ area, pool, gym, and function room.
Boyd Tower provides you access to an array of amazing restaurants including Oscars Table, Fish Bar, and Achelya Restaurant just to name a few, while The District Docklands, IGA supermarket, Marvel Stadium, Capital City Trail, and trams are only moments away!
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
Ultra Spacious Apartment with Uninterrupted Views
Located in a prime position where Docklands Meets the CBD, is this immaculately presented & spacious apartment in the Lacrosse complex. Welcoming ample natural light from level 15 & featuring a neutral & modern décor, this apartment incorporates a perfect blend convenience & style.
With an East-facing & ultra- spacious balcony that enjoys uninterrupted views of Melbourne's cityscape, the apartment is extremely well lit from dawn until dusk. Floor to ceiling windows throughout the living zone, this apartment features a bright and expansive open-plan living & dining area filled with abundant natural light which expands onto a well- appointed kitchen with stone bench tops, glass splash backs & stainless-steel appliances.
Both bedrooms are generously sized & feature built in robes with ample storage space. A Stylish central bathroom & separate ensuite, each with floor to ceiling tiles and high-end fittings.
Other features include European Laundry, reverse-cycle heating & cooling unit & double-glazed windows. Building amenities include fully equipped gymnasium, pool, private lift access, secure video-intercom entry & bicycle storage.
In a prime Location, just footsteps away from all that Melbourne has to offer without the commute. The vibrant Docklands Promenade restaurants & bars, Etihad stadium, Harbour town Shopping Centre & Southern Cross train station all only a short walk away, as well as a variety of CBD attractions. With transport options everywhere & trams right at your doorstep, this apartment makes an excellent investment opportunity or perfect new home

Description:
Rare 60sqm one bedroom apartment in the Gold Tower
If you want to ease into the property investment game with a smart and utterly stylish apartment that features outstanding quality and a fantastic NewQuay precinct location, then this 1 bedroom + study residence in the Gold Tower of the Aqui development is a prime opportunity.
North-facing and showcasing exceptional views which includes the Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, you get to enjoy sleek wooden floors, well-sized living and dining, superb balcony with views, stone kitchen with top of the range appliances, bedroom with northerly views and BIRs, study area, sleekly tiled bathroom with rain shower, laundry facilities, reverse cycle heating and cooling, and secure intercom entry. You also have access to a 25m indoor pool, spa, sauna, gym, library, private meeting rooms, and rooftop garden. Apart from investors, this property is also perfect to buy and live in youself!
The location is one of the best in the Docklands, where youre only a short walk to the scenic Victoria Harbour. You are also in close proximity to The District Docklands with great restaurants and entertainment including Hoyts Cinemas and GlowGolf, harbourside restaurants, Ron Barassi Snr Park, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and the 35, 70, and 86 trams.
Please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 485 860 to arrange and exclusive inspection

Description:
Breathtaking Living with unforgettable views in Yarra's Edge
Delivering an exceptional combination of space, style, and awe-inspiring views of the iconic Melbourne skyline, this breathtaking three bedroom, two bathroom Yarras Edge oasis is an absolute triumph.
You wont believe the immense space offered by the vast lounge and dining zone until you actually walk through it. This large living area also incorporates a lush stone kitchen with island bench and stainless steel appliances, while the amazing balcony runs the entire length of the apartment and showcases the marvelous vistas day and night.
All bedrooms have balcony access and a share in the views including the prized master bed with an elegant ensuite, while the central bathroom is striking in its modern style. A Euro laundry, ducted heat/cool, video intercom, an oversized storage cage, 2 car spaces, and access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, & sauna are other features.
Youre an easy stroll to a selection of stunning South Wharf restaurants and bars including Meat Market, The Boatbuilders Yard, The General Assembly, and Plus 5 Bar. Youre also near Crown Casino with world class entertainment, DFO shopping, IGA supermarket, and public transport including Southern Cross Station and trams on Spencer Street.
